Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.33,0:00:04.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertarungan Tonari melawan Nokker\Nterus berlanjut.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.96,0:00:07.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, lakukan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.55,0:00:13.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di tengah keputusasaan,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.09,0:00:15.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,teman-teman Fushi datang tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah aku tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sementara itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.56,0:00:25.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki dan yang lain
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.10,0:00:28.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyelamatkan "Mizuha" dari bawah tanah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Napa aku bisa memercayai kalian juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian mau minum air ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.64,0:02:26.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini simbol perjanjian yang diwariskan\Nturun-temurun oleh Pelindung.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pun yang ingin menjadi teman,\Nsahabat, maupun keluarga,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,harus minum air ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukti kita saling percaya\Nkapan pun dan di mana pun,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,serta takkan saling mengkhianati.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja. Ini cuma air biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.99,0:02:47.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kami meminumnya,\Nkau bakal ikut dengan kami, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yakin tak masalah meminum air ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.63,0:02:57.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan meminumnya, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan diminum!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, kita pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.70,0:03:25.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian semua yang di belakang,\Nikutlah ke rumahku juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Bon, tolong beri tahu Kakek
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau akan ada banyak orang\Nyang datang ke rumah kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ponselku rusak soalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki, kau ini lucu sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti sering terluka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau kulihat selalu bertindak\Ntanpa pikir panjang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau ini jebakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau airnya beracun?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki memang berani, tapi terlalu ceroboh.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sadar diri, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, airnya kau racuni?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia itu adik kelasku yang manis.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu benar-benar cuma air.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.86,0:04:06.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kutanya apa manusia dan Nokker\Nbisa hidup berdampingan dengan damai,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau bilang, "Tentu saja bisa."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.29,0:04:12.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masa aku bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pun lawan bicaraku,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan memercayai perkataan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Siapa pun lawan bicaranya"?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ini aku, Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya sudah kembali normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker sudah pergi,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi kita bisa minum airnya tanpa ragu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker masih ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi aku bicara dengan salah satunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, maksudmu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker masih bersembunyi di suatu tempat?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa namamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.12,0:04:51.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kan sudah kubilang, aku Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.54,0:04:57.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Mizuha bukan orang kidal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wakil Ketua!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertahanlah. Ayo kita ke tempat Satoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir, aku tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku masih harus belanja bahan\Nuntuk makan malam semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.58,0:05:39.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin Fushi akan membawa kembali\NNokker yang merasuki Kak Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.21,0:05:42.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kita bicarakan baik-baik,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.25,0:05:46.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku yakin mereka akan mengembalikan\Ntubuh Kak Mizuha dan yang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.97,0:05:51.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin kita bisa saling mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bahagia sekali, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Mizuha ada di sini,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,kira-kira bagaimana ya ekspresinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.69,0:06:04.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asal bisa membuatnya tersenyum lebar,\Nitu sudah cukup bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Pak Chamihiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jaga Kakek, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, tapi ada apa tiba-tiba?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.49,0:06:58.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu ingin\Nbertarung serius denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.87,0:07:01.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari buktikan siapa yang lebih kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira kau akan kembali ke Surga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ambisimu sudah terpenuhi sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.41,0:07:41.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kupikirkan\Nsetelah kau mengalahkanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.14,0:07:58.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir bisa menghentikanku begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terlalu lambat!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.29,0:08:29.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau menahan diri?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.81,0:08:46.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku melawanmu sepenuh hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.86,0:08:56.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau terpengaruh oleh Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lumayan suka padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.75,0:09:06.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia meminum air berisi Nokker tanpa ragu
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,demi membuktikan pertemanan kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kemampuanmu cuma segini?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita sudah melangkah sejauh ini,\Nkurasa itu sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ambil senjatamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Busur atau pedang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki memang memengaruhiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak ingin membunuhmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alangkah menyenangkannya
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau kita bisa berdamai\Nselagi masih sama-sama hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini belum berakhir, Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau memindahkan intimu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir bisa mengalahkanku\Npakai tubuh itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sungguh berniat melawanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus aku yang tanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.13,0:10:40.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau tak kedinginan memakai baju\Nyang terbuat dari kulit itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau dilanjut, Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.49,0:11:00.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan kira omongan sok sucimu\Nbisa memengaruhiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih bersikeras?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengajakmu bicara alih-alih membunuhmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa itu terdengar\Nseperti omongan sok suci bagimu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajar kalau manusia berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.46,0:11:15.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kita bukan manusia, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.05,0:11:19.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, Chami.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.63,0:11:22.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukannya masih banyak amunisi\Ndi gudang, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.97,0:11:26.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha, mau Ayah bantu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak usah, Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia belum mengerahkan kekuatan aslinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mengganggunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.06,0:11:37.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua wujud tempur Fushi\Nsudah kuambil.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang cuma tersisa yang tak berguna.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, mau pakai ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak usah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nlawanlah dia dengan serius.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.29,0:11:50.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti masih punya\Nsatu wujud lagi, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.79,0:11:55.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menyembunyikannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarkan sekarang juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak menyembunyikan apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma menunggu waktu yang tepat\Nuntuk menghadapimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penerus Keenam.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kahaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,wujud tak berguna!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan kubiarkan\Nkau menghina rekan-rekanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadapilah aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan salah paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, hunus pedangmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alasan kau begitu kuat
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,karena darah klanmu\Nmengalir di tubuh itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakit!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kau belum terbiasa\Ndengan rasa sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dilihat dari hal itu,\Nkau belum siap mati, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau tak punya tempat tujuan,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.71,0:13:24.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,bersemayamlah di tubuhku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku melakukannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan merebut semua wadahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belum pernah mencobanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.23,0:13:37.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi entah sekuat apa aku mampu\Nmenahan sosok asing sepertimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kalau kau lebih kuat dariku,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan kucari cara mengatasinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak pernah memikirkan\Nkonsekuensinya dulu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.\NIntinya sudah kuhancurkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa ini saatnya kita pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingin rasanya menyingkirkanmu,\Ntapi intimu tak bisa kutemukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.27,0:14:17.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bahkan tak bisa memanggil\Nsosok penciptamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertarungan kita di masa kini\Nsudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertarungan di "masa kini"?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya masih berlanjut.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami juga menjalani hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.36,0:14:30.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia datang ke sini untuk dibunuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk memulai kembali dari awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Air di sini sudah terkontaminasi Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan lupa dibilas.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.75,0:14:41.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu mengalir ke laut,\Nhidup mati mereka kuserahkan pada takdir.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan salah paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan berarti kau yang menang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, syukurlah kali ini aku ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat ini seperti labirin, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat juga Fushi dan yang lain\Nbisa sampai sejauh ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.96,0:15:24.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, kita di mana sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Air.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan, Anda tersesat?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.90,0:15:45.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kalian berdua\Nyang bakal menunjukkan jalannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kan sudah kubilang,\Nkami tak ingat jalannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.70,0:15:52.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat, bagaimana kalau aku tersesat?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bawa bekal air maupun makanan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan, tenanglah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami punya makanan dan air kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah? Syukurlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua kan hantu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan, syukurlah. Ada air!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau air seperti ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus! Itu pintu keluarnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pintu masuknya, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niatnya mencari Fushi,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,malah kembali ke titik awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bon.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, syukurlah kau selamat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana? Sudah beres semua?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beres semua?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.54,0:16:51.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku gagal menyelesaikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.84,0:16:55.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya sudah tak bisa diubah lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini wujud cadangan untuk jaga-jaga?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak pernah menggunakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.24,0:17:13.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, saatnya berangkat ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekolah?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bon, aku pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuai keinginan kalian,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tak membunuh para Nokker.\NAku mengurung mereka di dalam sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah ini,\Nmereka akan dilepaskan ke laut
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan kubiarkan mereka\Nmemutuskan tempat tinggalnya sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, bagaimana dengan Tonari?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonari sudah mati.\NDia dibunuh dengan kejam.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa wajah kalian begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bersedih hanya karena aku mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.99,0:18:01.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,To... Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian pasti terkejut, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.00,0:18:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak bernama Satoru itu\Nmenghidupkanku kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, siapa anak itu? Kau mengenalnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku. Pasti rasanya sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini semua salahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bodoh!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau meminta maaf\Nuntuk hal semacam itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang paling penting...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,katakan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita kan sudah berteman ratusan tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.64,0:18:27.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong andalkanlah kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti kau akan kuomeli.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bu Tana!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah masih hidup!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami yang melakukannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami melawan penjahatnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.41,0:19:23.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aneh. Tak ada siapa pun di rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum ada yang pulang satu pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok bisa begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bau beruang juga tak tercium.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak kusangka\Nhari ini bakal tiba.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, berapa takar beras\Nyang harus kumasak?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.35,0:19:46.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakek, maaf membuatmu menunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bawa banyak tamu, nih.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, Kakek setidaknya harus masak\Nseratus takar beras!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa orang-orang di belakangmu ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Pak Bon tak memberitahumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakek! Kak Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kau selamat!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini? Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kujelaskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.38,0:20:19.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi sebelum itu, ayo makan malam dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.14,0:20:26.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, apinya menyala dan meledak!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.97,0:20:30.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami melawan mati-matian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kondisinya parah banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.52,0:20:35.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian lumayan hebat juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini semua berkat Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.44,0:20:41.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aiko jauh lebih hebat dariku, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia punya ide dan eksekusi\Nyang bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, itu tidak benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.74,0:20:50.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan bisa melakukan apa-apa\Ntanpa kakak-kakak kelas sekalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan diminum, Satoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia Sosok Hitam\Nyang diceritakan Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sulit dipercaya,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.01,0:21:04.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku sendiri melihatnya punya\Nkekuatan untuk mengusir Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Garam bisa melukai Nokker?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah memastikan garam suci\Nefektif menangkal Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayangnya, itu cuma efek pengusir.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuh, kan? Coba tadi kau biarkan aku\Nmenaburinya dengan garam.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.06,0:21:19.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf. Lain kali kubiarkan\Nkau saja yang melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.48,0:21:20.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lain kali?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Aku tidak mau lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.24,0:21:27.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Gaya tabur garammu tadi keren, kok.\N- Kerja sama tim kita bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Memangnya aku bilang hal yang aneh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.25,0:21:34.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan, ini sama sekali\Nbukan kerja sama tim.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, tadi kami kan bertengkar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sama sekali tak akur.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,\Napa yang kau lakukan waktu itu, Hanna?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudengar kau pergi ke suatu tempat\Nbersama Yuki dan yang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.51,0:21:51.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu... Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.35,0:21:54.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi aku pergi untuk...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,membawa pulang Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tak berhasil membawanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.99,0:22:10.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, makanlah yang banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.46,0:22:23.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat makan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Mizuha!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.44,0:22:41.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sudah menunggumu, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.44,0:22:42.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.48,0:22:43.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.57,0:22:44.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.91,0:22:50.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah melakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.88,0:24:37.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi mencari cara\Nuntuk hidup berdampingan dengan Nokker,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.76,0:24:42.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki pun mengajak seseorang berbicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:43.35,0:24:45.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah kehilangan tujuannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.98,0:24:49.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi mulai merasa bimbang.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.61,0:24:52.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akankah dia menerima kekuatan barunya?
